---
---

<section id="tarifs" class="py-24 bg-[#FDFBF7] relative">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block text-artisan-accent font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4">
        Transparence Totale
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-artisan-text mb-6">
        Des tarifs clairs, sans mauvaises surprises.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-artisan-muted font-sans">
        En tant qu'entrepreneur individuel, vous bénéficiez de <strong>tarifs nets</strong> (TVA non applicable). Ce que vous voyez sur le devis est exactement ce que vous payez.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-stretch">
      
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-artisan-text/10 xl:p-10 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md duration-300">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-4">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-artisan-text">Site Vitrine Signature</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-artisan-muted font-sans">
            Un site ultra-rapide et optimisé pour transformer vos visiteurs en clients. Paiement unique à la livraison.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mt-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-artisan-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">À partir de</p>
            <p class="flex items-baseline gap-x-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black text-artisan-text tracking-tight">1 890 €</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-artisan-muted">Net</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-artisan-muted font-sans">
            <li class="flex gap-x-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-artisan-accent font-bold">✓</span>
              Design sur-mesure (pas de modèle tout fait)
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-artisan-accent font-bold">✓</span>
              Optimisation SEO (pour Google)
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-artisan-accent font-bold">✓</span>
              Score de performance garanti (100/100)
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-artisan-accent font-bold">✓</span>
              Conformité RGPD incluse
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#contact" class="mt-8 block rounded-lg px-3 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-artisan-text ring-1 ring-inset ring-artisan-text/20 hover:bg-artisan-text/5 transition-colors">Obtenir un devis précis</a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-3xl bg-artisan-text p-8 shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-900/10 xl:p-10 relative overflow-hidden transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl duration-300">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4 w-24 h-24 bg-artisan-accent rounded-full opacity-20 blur-xl"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-x-4">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-white">Pack "Sérénité"</h3>
            <span class="rounded-full bg-artisan-accent/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold leading-5 text-artisan-accent border border-artisan-accent/30">Indispensable</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 font-sans">
            Vous faites votre métier, je m'occupe de votre site. Hébergement, sécurité et mises à jour gérés de A à Z.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mt-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-artisan-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">À partir de</p>
            <p class="flex items-baseline gap-x-1">
              <span class="text-4xl font-black text-white tracking-tight">40 €</span>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-400">Net / mois</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 mt-1">Engagement de 12 mois</p>
          </div>
          
          <ul role="list" class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300 font-sans">
            <li class="flex gap-x-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">✓</span>
              Hébergement sécurisé en France
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">✓</span>
              Sauvegardes automatiques hebdomadaires
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">✓</span>
              Rapport de statistiques (Matomo)
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-x-3 items-start">
              <span class="text-white font-bold">✓</span>
              Petites modifications de texte offertes
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#contact" class="mt-8 block rounded-lg bg-artisan-accent px-3 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-artisan-accent-hover focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 transition-colors relative z-10">En savoir plus</a>
      </div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl mt-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 ring-1 ring-artisan-text/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 transition-all hover:shadow-md">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-artisan-text text-xl">Applications Métiers & Sur-mesure</h3>
          <p class="text-artisan-muted text-sm mt-2">Outil de facturation, portail client, automatisation... Je développe des outils métiers robustes (Next.js).</p>
          <p class="text-artisan-text font-bold mt-2">À partir de 3 990 € Net</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#contact" class="whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-artisan-text ring-1 ring-inset ring-artisan-text/20 hover:bg-artisan-text/5 transition-colors">
          Étude sur devis
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>